Commit labels
--------------------------

A commit message must be formated as follow

[SECTION] Description

Where section is:
    - HARD: the commit is about hardware modifications (schematic, board, ...)
    - SOFT: the commit is about software modifications (code, toolchain script, ...)
    - TEXT: the commit is about text files
    - OTHER

File formatting
--------------------------

All files must be indented with expanded tabs (4 spaces)
